  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nerigon version 2022.99.99-dev-63fa65cf\r\n\r\n#### Behavior\r\nWhen I called `eth_estimateGas`, it could not find the block header.\r\n\r\n`ValueError: {'code': -32000, 'message': 'block 14917087(a62c8a3c98465abaabc2d60e9b067a4e05634791e7627b787a094b35a5e7af31) not found'}`\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behavior\r\nWe can reproduce this behavior with this script.\r\n`w3.eth.estimate_gas({\"to\":\"0xB4e16d0168e52d35CaCD2c6185b44281Ec28C9Dc\", \"data\": \"0x0902f1ac\"}, 14917087)`\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Solution\r\nI think the bug might be due to the fact that `rawdb.ReadHeader()` is deprecated. In order to fix the bug in `estimateGas`. We can replace `HeaderByNumberOrHash` by the following\r\n\r\n```\r\nblockNum, _, _, err := rpchelper.GetBlockNumber(bNrOrHash, dbtx, api.filters)\r\nif err != nil {\r\n\treturn 0, err\r\n}\r\nblock, err := api.blockByNumberWithSenders(dbtx, blockNum)\r\nif err != nil {\r\n\treturn 0, err\r\n}\r\nh := block.Header()\r\n```\r\n",
